<author>mrym fhmy, rạjy kmạl</author>
<title>bḥkmtk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bḥkmtk tdbr kl sẖyʾ tmlk
 ḥyạty wtrtb ly ạlkẖyr
 tmnʿ ʿny ạlkẖṭr wtstr ʿly̱ ʿywby bḥbk ạlkbyr
 ạlqrạr- ḥkmtk ạ̉kbr dlyl tbny kl sẖyʾ fy
 ạldnyạ ʿndk btdbyr
 btdbyrk ḥqqt lynạ ạlwʿd wmn ḥnạnk nzlt ʿly̱
 ạlạ̉rḍ
 wlạ̉ ḥbk kbyr mạhmksẖ mzwd fqyr
 2- bqdrtk qạmt ạ̉mwạt wḥbybk lʿạzr mạt
 fy ạlqbr lyh tlạt ạ̉yạm qwmth yạ rby bslạm
 3- wlmạ yạ ạ̹lhy ṣlbwk wbḥrbẗ yạ ạ̹lhy ṭʿnwk
 bḥkmẗ nwrt ʿywnhm wnạs ậmnt byk wḥbwk</lyrics>
</song>